title: Starts of the Week + Week 2 Breakdown, Elijah Missile! - Fantasy Football Podcast for 9/16
description:
Week 2 is here and The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, get Starts of the Week from Andy, Mike, and Jason! Plus, a number of Week 2 matchup breakdowns, a new edition of “Never Not Working!” Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for September 16th, 2021.
  
 (06:55) - Never Not Working
 (14:20) - NFL News
 (22:40) - Week 2 Matchups
 (22:50) - Bengals at Bears 
 (27:35) - Texans at Browns
 (31:35) - Rams at Colts
 (35:05) - Bills at Dolphins
 (40:55) - Patriots at Jets
 (45:05) - 49ers at Eagles
